<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Task Deletion Notification</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4;">

  <table role="presentation" style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; margin: 20px auto; border-radius: 10px; border: 2px solid #81c3c9; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 30px; text-align: center;">
        
        

        <!-- Header -->
        <h1 style="font-size: 24px; color: #1e3653; margin: 0;">Task Deletion Notification</h1>
<br/>
        <!-- Message -->
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e3653; text-align: left; margin-top: 20px;">
          Hello <%= @volunteer.first_name %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e3653; text-align: left;">
          We wanted to inform you that a task which you had accepted for <strong><%= @senior.first_name %> <%= @senior.last_name %></strong>, has been deleted by them.
        </p>
        <table style="width: 50%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; border-radius: 10px; text-align:center; border: 3px double #81c3c9;">
        <tr>
        <td>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;  color: #1e3653;">
        <strong>Task:</strong> <%= @task.task_type %><br/>
        <strong>Task ID:</strong> <%= @task.id %><br/>
        <% if @task.description.present? %>
         <strong>Description:</strong> <%= @task.description %>
        <% end %>
        
        </p>       
        </td>
      </tr>
      </table>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e3653; text-align: left;">
          If you have any questions or require further clarification, please don't hesitate to contact us.
        </p>

        <!-- Closing -->
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1e3653; text-align: left;">
          Best regards,<br/><br/>
          <strong>The Handy Heroes Team</strong>
        </p>

        <!-- Divider -->
        <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #f37022; margin: 20px 0;">

        <!-- Footer -->
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #1e3653; text-align: center; font-style: italic;">
          <strong>Handy Heroes... Connecting Communities, One Task at a Time!</strong>
        </p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>

</body>
</html>
